<div class="row mb-3">
    <h2 class="text-center heading-color font-weight-bold">The Silent Crisis: Animals Consuming Plastic</h2>
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p class="heading-color">
            In the pristine wilderness of our planet, a silent crisis is unfolding. From the depths of the oceans to the vast savannas, animals are consuming plastic, a man-made material that has permeated every corner of our natural world. This growing environmental disaster poses a grave threat to wildlife and ecosystems, and its ripple effects are increasingly visible and alarming.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
